Double Punch/Injector/Manterror/Bumblebee:




Double Punch ducked under Airbomber's shot, going into his stealth mode, 
cloaked, he did a few flips backwards.

---

Manterror grunted as the shot connected with him, the green Predacon firing 
off four ion disks (two from each "clawed hand") at Airbomber's chest.

---

Injector fell back a foot, firing off two stinger missiles from his launcher 
at Airbomber's abdomen.

---

Bumblebee launched into the air, Airbomber's shots missing him.  The Predacon 
quickly gained altitude.
